OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FRemaining
OL,6,Fdry this evening with plenty of late
OL,7,Fevening sunshine. Overnight may see
OL,8,Fsome patchy cloud to the far east or a
OL,9,Ffew mist patches reform but most
OL,10,Fremaining clear. Staying warm with
OL,11,Ftemperatures.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSaturday:FThe heatwave continues on
OL,14,FSaturday with another dry and sunny
OL,15,Fday. Feeling hot with high UV but
OL,16,Fperhaps a more notable breeze
OL,17,Fdeveloping later in the day.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
